ually in my mind. \u00a0Going to work, turning on my computer, travelling, meeting, grafting&#8230;I am holding the needs of children in my heart.<\/p>\n<p>For some reason, this makes me happy. \u00a0Children are the best clients.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Looking back over my work in the past five years, there are two projects that stand out as the most enjoyable. \u00a0The jobs that have made me happiest\u00a0have been designing the content for:<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2861,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[48,101,190,202,205],"class_list":["post-1752","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-business","tag-children","tag-heart","tag-technology","tag-work","tag-writing"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1752"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1752"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1752\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4385,"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1752\/revisions\/4385"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2861"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1752"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1752"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/joind.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1752"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/